1. Tng quan
Ngy nay, c hng t thit b c kt ni Internet v iu ny dn n
thc y nhiu tin b vt bc trong s pht trin ca cng ngh in t v vin
thng trong nhng nm gn y. Kt qu l cho ra i nhiu loi thit b c kh
nng giao tip v kt ni rt mnh m thu ht cc ngnh cng nghip p dng
cng ngh vo hot ng kinh doanh, sn xut hng ngy ca h nhm tng hiu
sut cng vic. Ngoi lnh vc cng nghip cn c cc lnh vc khc nh dch v
h tr sinh hot, dch v cng cng, v.v... c nhu cu ln v pht trin cng ngh
thng tin v truyn thng. Do , cn c mt m hnh mi trong giao tip my vi
my - Machine-to-Machine (M2M) cho php kt ni vn vt (Things) vo mng
li Internet ton cu. M hnh ny c bit n vi thut ng IoT (Internet of
Things).
IoT l mng li cc vt th vt l hay "vn vt" c nhng cc thit b
in t, phn mm, cc cm bin v cc kt ni cho php chng cung cp cc dch
v v mang li nhiu gi tr bng cch trao i d liu vi nh sn xut, cc bn
iu hnh v/hoc cc thit b c kt ni khc thng qua cc giao thc truyn
thng tin m khng cn c s vn hnh ca con ngi.
Bng cch kt ni hng t, thm ch hng nghn t thit b vi Internet,
chng ta thy rng c rt nhiu ng dng ang c s dng bi chnh ph, cc
ngnh cng nghip hay truy cp cng cng, v.v... Ly v d ng dng h thng giao
thng thng minh (Intelligent Transport System - ITS) gim st giao thng trong
thnh ph bng cc cm bin khng dy hoc thng qua cc video gim st v gi
thng tin n ngi dng trn thit b di ng ca h vi s tr gip ca h thng
13
nh v ton cu (GPS) gip ngi dng phng trnh kt xe v phng nga tai
nn. y ch l mt v d ng dng trong s rt rt nhiu ng dng khc nh nh
thng minh hay chm sc sc kho. Mt lng ln d liu ang c to ra bi
hng t thit b c kt ni v truyn qua mng Internet.
Trong IoT, cc thit b u cui ng vai tr quan trng l cc thit b th
cm mi trng v sinh ra d liu. Tuy nhin do kh nng tnh ton yu km ca
chng, cc thit b ny thng gi d liu ti cc nt m my lu tr, x l,
phn tch cng nh a ra cc quyt nh iu khin. Mt trong nhng li ch ca
vic tch hp ny l s linh hot m ngi dng c c khi truy cp cc dch v
c cung cp thng qua giao din web. iu ny cng mang li s linh hot cho
cc nh cung cp dch v M2M d dng em dch v ca mnh ti nhiu khch
hng hn. in ton m my thng l m hnh cho php s dng mng thun
tin, tu theo nhu cu ca ngi s dng v mt nhm ti nguyn my tnh (mng,
my ch, lu tr, tnh ton, ng dng, dch v...) mt cch nhanh chng. Tuy nhin
do s khng ng nht v kim sot lng lo ca Internet, nhiu vn pht sinh
c bit l cht lng dch v kh c th m bo c. Cc ng dng thi gian
thc c ngi dng tng tc trc tip chu nh hng xu bi tr mng. Mt
im na m in ton m my phi i mt l bo mt v quyn ring t. D liu
ngi dng nm trn cc m my cng cng c nguy c b xm phm tnh ton
vn v tnh bo mt. Cc h thng m my c th b tn cng bng mt s phng
php khc nhau. Nh vy c th thy cc h thng m my phi ng trc nhiu
mi e do bo mt khc nhau do chng c trin khai trn Inter net.
Khc phc nhng nhc im trn, in ton sng m ra i, c lu
tr ti gia cc thit b cui v m my. Cc nt sng m c th l cc switch,
gateway, cc my tnh nh (mini-computer) hay chnh nhng chic in thoi di
ng. Chng c mt s chc nng nh truyn ti d liu t cc thit b u cui
ln cc m my, thu thp, lu tr v x l d liu i vi cc tc v yu cu c
thc hin trong thi gian thc, c tr thp. in ton sng m cho php IoT c
tnh di ng cao vi phn b rng khp, thm vo l kh nng nhn bit v tr
v tr thp. Hn th, bng vic kt hp c vi cc m my c, ta c c h

thng in ton v cng mnh m, in ton sng m - m my. Tng sng m

Hnh 1.1: in ton sng m - m my
(https://cs.uni-paderborn.de/fileadmin/infor matik/fg/ce/Teaching/Project_groups/EML.pdf)
Vi cc thnh phn c m t trn (thit b u cui, tng sng m v
tng m my), vic lp lch tc v cho cc yu cu x l d liu trong cc h thng
sng m - m my tr thnh mt bi ton thch thc v phc tp. L do chnh l
s khc bit v kh nng tnh ton cng nh lu tr ca cc nt sng m v m
my. Do s khc bit ca mi loi tnh ton, c nhiu yu t nh hng n thit
k v hot ng ca mi trng sng m - m my. V d, cc nt sng m
thng c ngun nng lng b gii hn (c cung cp bi pin, c quy...); chng
c th x l d liu rt nhanh nh khong cch ngn gia chng v cc thit b u
cui. Ngc li, mc d cc m my cung cp kh nng thc hin cc tc v vi
hiu nng cao, tr trong vic truyn d liu li ng cn nhc. Bn cnh ,
chi ph vn hnh, s dng dch v l yu t rt c ngi s dng v nh cung
cp quan tm. Ngi dng cn s dng cc dch v vi chi ph nh nht cn nh
cung cp dch v khng ch chi ph vn hnh m cn l s dng sao cho ph hp,
15
tit kim vi h tng hin c. Theo , chin lc lp lch trong h thng cn phi
tho mn c nhiu yu cu, rng buc h thng hot ng hiu qu, ti u.
Bi v vy, bi ton lp lch l mt bi ton quan trng trong bt k h thng in
ton chia s ti nguyn no.
Lun vn ny thc hin m hnh ho h thng sng m - m my vi cc
rng buc khc nhau v mi trng. Theo cch ny, lun vn xem xt ba rng buc
chnh gm: in nng tiu th, tr dch v v chi ph s dng da trn cc chc
nng m cc nt sng m, m my thc hin (truyn d liu, tnh ton, lu tr
v x l). Lun vn cng nh ngha mt hm mc tiu c dng ti u ho bi
ton lp lch da trn m hnh sng m - m my xut. Chng ti thc
hin mt s th nghim vi cc phng php metaheuristic nhm chng minh tnh
ng n ca m hnh ny. Cng vi trnh by mi quan h gia ba rng buc
trong qu trnh ti u ho. Mc d c mt s nghin cu v vn lp lch tc v
trong m trng sng m - m my, vn cn cha c nghin cu no xem xt c
ba rng buc nu trn.
Nhng kt qu ca lun vn chnh l nhng kt qu c chp nhn v
cng b ti hi ngh quc t IEEE International Symposium on Network Comput-
ing and Applications (IEEE NCA) ln th 19 vo thng 11/2020 [2].
ng gp ca nghin cu:
1. M hnh ho mi trng nhiu rng buc ca cc h thng in ton sng
m - m my gm in nng tiu th, tr dch v v chi ph.
2. xut s dng cc gii thut metaheuristic gii bi ton lp lch trong m
hnh sng m - m my xut.
3. Gi lp h thng sng m - m my nh xut nh gi cc chin
lc lp lch tc v trn .
4. Th nghim vi mt s gii thut metaheuristic cho bi ton lp lch trong mi
trng nhiu rng buc ca h thng sng m - m my.

2.1.2 Cc c trng
Tnh linh hot ca in ton m my l phn pht ti nguyn tu theo nhu
cu. iu ny to ra kh nng mm do, thun li cho vic s dng ti nguyn ca
h thng, loi b s rng buc phi u t phn cng c th cho mi nhim v.
Trc khi c in ton m my, cc trang web hoc ng dng c chy trn mt
my ch c th hot ng trong mt h thng. Vi s ra i ca in ton m my,
cc ti nguyn c hp nht v s dng nh kho chung. Cu hnh hp nht ny
cung cp mt mi trng cc ng dng thc hin mt cch c lp m khng
quan tm n bt k cu hnh c th no. Vin Tiu chun v Cng ngh cng nh
ngha nm c trng ct li ca m hnh in ton m my:
Dch v cung cp theo nhu cu (On-demand self-service): Ngi dng t mua,
t thu, t cu hnh trin khai cc dch v in ton m my theo cc chun
nh sn (template) m khng cn ti s tr gip ca b phn IT. lm c

Cc chun ny cha cc cu hnh c nh ngha trc, cn c vo ngi
dng s tu chnh thm v ci t cc dch v theo nhu cu.
Tr uy cp mng bng thng cao (Broad network access): Ti nguyn tnh ton
lun sn sng ton mng v c truy cp thng qua cc chun mng.
Ti nguyn khng gii hn (Resource pooling): Nh cung cp d tr cc ti
nguyn tnh ton chia s cho nhiu ngi s dng bng m hnh multi-

Dch v o lng (Measured Service): Cc h thng in ton m my t

c mc tru tng ph hp vi cc dch v. Lng s dng ti nguyn c
gim st, iu khin v thng k hon ton trong sut vi cc nh cung cp v

Tu thuc vo hnh thc cung cp v nhu cu s dng m in ton m

4. m my lai (Hybrid cloud) l mt t hp ca hai hay nhiu m my (ni

2.3 Bi ton lp lch
2.3.1 nh ngha

2.3.2 c trng
Khi nghin cu v bi ton lp lch cn lm r cc c trng c bn ca bi
ton. Cc c trng c bn bao gm: ti nguyn, tc v, rng buc v mc tiu.
1. Ti nguyn: l cc ngun d liu u vo ca bi ton. Cc ti nguyn ny
c th phc hi hoc khng.
2. Tc v: c nh gi qua cc tiu chun thc hin nh thi gian thc hin,
chi ph, mc tiu th ngun ti nguyn.
3. Rng buc: y l nhng iu kin cn tho mn bi ton c th a ra li
gii tt nht.
4. Mc tiu: nh gi ti u ca li gii bi ton. Khi cc mc tiu c tho
mn th cc rng buc cng phi c tho mn.

Vn rng buc ti nguyn trong bi ton lp lch rt a dng v phc tp.

Nguyn l th t: Thc hin hnh ng da trn mt cu trc th t hp l

Hnh 2.5: Gii thut di truyn
(https://pastmike.com/what-is-a-genetic-algorithm/)
Gii thut di truyn l mt gii thut da trn c ch ca chn lc tin ho
trong t nhin: "Trong mi th h, mt tp mi cc sinh vt c to ra bng cch
lai ghp nhng nhn t thch nghi nht vi mi trng ca nhng sinh vt trong th

Vn dng c ch , gii thut di truyn c bt u vi mt qun th ngu nhin
c n chui, ri sao chp cc chui theo khuynh hng hng n ci tt, ghp cp
v i cc chui con thnh phn, thnh thong lm t bin gi tr bit.
Theo xut ban u ca gio s John Holland, mt vn , bi ton t
ra s c m ha thnh cc chui bit vi chiu di c nh. Ni mt cch chnh
xc l cc thng s ca bi ton s c chuyn i v biu din li di dng cc
chui nh phn. Cc thng s ny c th l cc bin ca mt hm hoc h s ca

c th, cc genome u c cng chiu di. Ni ngn gn, mt li gii s c biu

ca c th vy. Nh vy, i vi thut gii di truyn, mt c th ch c mt gen
duy nht v mt gen cng ch phc v cho mt c th duy nht.
Ban u, pht sinh mt tp hp cc chui bit ngu nhin. Tp cc c th ny
c gi l qun th ban u (initial population). Sau , xc nh mt gi tr gi

ca qun th, c hai thao tc:
u tin l sao chp nguyn mu mt nhm cc c th tt t th h trc a
sang th h sau. Thao tc ny m bo thch nghi ca th h sau lun c

Th hai l to ra cc cc th mi bng cch thc hin cc thao tc sinh sn

2.3.4 Bi ton lp lch trong in ton sng m - m my
Trong in ton m my v in ton sng m, c rt nhiu gii thut
metaheur istic c p dng hiu qu cho bi ton lp lch. C mt s gii thut
metaheur istic ni ting c th k n nh: Gii thut di truyn (Genetic Algorithm
- GA) [23] v gii thut by n (Particle Swarm Optimization - PSO) [24]. Gn
y c gii thut c voi (Whale Optimization Algorithm - WOA) [22] cng tr
thnh mt phng php in hnh chng minh hiu nng cnh tranh khi so snh
vi nhng phng php khc ni trn. Theo mi trng chy ca cc chin lc
lp lch tc v, lun vn phn loi cc nghin cu c thnh ba nhm gm cc h
thng m my, h thng sng m v h thng sng m - m my.
Nhiu nghin cu gii quyt vi cc bi ton lp lch tc v v phn b
ti nguyn cho m my s dng cc phng php khc nhau. Trong [25], [26],
v [27], cc tc gi xut trin khai cc k thut m v hc my phn tch
v d on khi lng cng vic nhm a ra cc quyt nh m rng, co gin ti
nguyn. Trong khi , hng i v l thuyt tr chi c p dng cho cc bi
ton lp lch h thng [28], [29]. Cc tc gi ca [30], [31], [32], [33] xut chin
lc qun l cc cng vic cn x l s dng cc phng php PSO, GA v WOA.
Mt s nghin cu c gng m hnh ho mi trng sng m vi cc
42
c tnh ca n. Trong [34] v [35], cc tc gi ch ra rng cc c im ca m

thit b cui. Tuy nhin, h li cha a ra bt c gii php no cho bi ton lp

Trong mi trng IoT, vi s tch hp ca in ton sng m v m my,

dng mi trng sng m - m my vi cc rng buc khc nhau l mt c s

Round-Robin, Min-Min hay Max-Min. Round-Robin l gii thut lp lch c nht,
n gin nht khi cc tc v c gn cho tng nt theo th t vng trn m khng
c u tin no. Min-Min nhiu phc tp hn Round-Robin. N bt u vi mt

gn cho ti nguyn tng ng. Tc v ny sau c xo b khi tp hp v qu
tr nh c lp li cho n khi tt c cc tc v c nh x ti ti nguyn hp l.
Cng tng t Min-Min, ngoi tr pha th hai, Max-Min gn cc tc v vi thi

gian hon thnh d kin ln nht vo cc ti nguyn tng ng. Trong khi , cc
